hu.akarnokd.reactive4java.reactive

Class Windowing.WithTime<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.akarnokd.reactive4java.reactive.Windowing.WithTime<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the source element type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Observable<Observable<T>>
    Enclosing class:
    Windowing

    public static class Windowing.WithTime<T>
extends Object
implements Observable<Observable<T>>
    Projects elements from the source observable into zero or more windows which are produced based on timing information.

    The implementation ensures that if timespan and timeshift are equal, the windows won't overlap.

    Author:
    akarnokd, 2013.01.17.
